</H5>

<s docid="FBIS4-1213" num="87"> Registered to contest: National and all nine regions PLATFORM: The ACDP says it represents the following: a fresh start, uncontaminated by the past; a diverse leadership, united behind common Christian principles to bring hope and vision to the nation; a genuine federal framework or self-governance with maximum constitutional powers at the lowest possible level, and an open-market economy.</s>
