</H5>

<s docid="FBIS4-1213" num="96"> Registered to contest: National and all nine regions PLATFORM: The AMCP believes the country must be managed like a company where government positions will be filled by experienced, qualified and competent persons with proven track records, regardless of their party political affiliations.</s>

<s docid="FBIS4-1213" num="97"> The voters, as shareholders, will measure the dividends of this strategy in the general economic prosperity of the country, says its policy statement.</s>

