</H5>

<s docid="FBIS4-1213" num="113"> Registered to contest: National and PWV region PLATFORM: Kendall stresses federalism above all.</s>

<s docid="FBIS4-1213" num="114"> She believes in the devolution of power and in direct democracy.</s>

<s docid="FBIS4-1213" num="115"> The electorate should be encouraged and allowed to vote on issues on an ongoing basis.</s>

<s docid="FBIS4-1213" num="116"> The Federal Party believes central government should have power only over defence, finance, foreign affairs and the Appeal Court.</s>

